c: 7
v: 44
t: "Ke kaloku abahlali basePaladesi baza kukhwaza abahlali baseMlilweni\t(bathi):\t“Thina\tsikufumene\tkuyinyaniso oko sakuthenjiswa yiNkosi yethu; ingaba nani nikufumene kuyinyaniso oko iNkosi yenu yanithembisa ngako”? Baya kuthi bona: “Ewe” Umkhwazi uya kumemeza phakathi kwabo:“Isiqalekisosika-Allâhmasibephezukwabagabadeli.”"